cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about facial image super-resolution and deblurring using a generative adversarial network. The most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image processing and analysis. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper uses a generative adversarial network for image generation. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper uses deep learning techniques for image processing. The fourth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with image and video processing. The fifth likely category is cs.GR (Graphics) as the paper deals with image generation and reconstruction.
